These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, black, yellow, lilac
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, bridge, chess
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, cola, milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who likes lilac##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person who likes lilac is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking milk is between the person playing chess and the person who likes ivory##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Color         | lilac      | ivory | black | yellow |
| Game   | bridge | canasta  | whist   | chess    |
| Beverage     | soy-milk     | cola    | milk    | sprite      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, lemonade, coffee
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, emerald, grey, ebony
There 4 different types of food: garlic, broccoli, pear, kale
1. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
2. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes grey##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
4. the person eating garlic is on the far right##1
5. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
7. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking mirinda##2
8. the person who likes ebony is between the person who likes emerald and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage         | coffee | lemonade   | mirinda | tea  |
| Color   | grey     | aquamarine | ebony  | emerald |
| Food     | kale        | pear  | broccoli    | garlic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, backgammon, bridge
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, crime, animation, western
City: hamburg, london, new-york, liverpool
1. the person watching western movies is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing bridge##2
2. the person watching crime movies is the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching animation movies is between the person playing scrabble and the person watching time-travel movies##2
7. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | monopoly | scrabble   | bridge     | backgammon     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | western | animation   | time-travel  |
| City     | liverpool      | london | new-york | hamburg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, writing
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, australian, polish
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, zucchini, lemon, asparagus
1. the polish is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the indian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
5. the polish is the person eating cabbage##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the german##1
7. the australian is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | traveling  | writing   | rock-climbing     | magic-tricks |
| Nationality   | australian  | polish      | german        | indian     |
| Food         | lemon | cabbage | asparagus | zucchini   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, traveling, skydiving, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, classical, salsa, metal
4 different pets are kept: lizard, horse, goat, dog
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the fan of metal##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is the fan of metal##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
6. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
9. the fan of funk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Hobby   | reading   | sudoku   | skydiving | traveling |
| Music-Genre         | classical      | metal | funk      | salsa |
| Pet     | horse | lizard        | dog       | goat  |

