.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, backgammon, whist
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, mauve, aquamarine
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, july, september
1. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
8. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Game    | backgammon   | whist      | monopoly       | mah-jongg |
| Color   | light-blue | aquamarine | mauve     | fuchsia |
| Birthday     | september     | june  | january | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, november, september, february
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, paramedic, doctor, mechanic
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, ivory, azure, chestnut
1. the person who likes azure is the dancer##1
2. the person who likes ivory is between the mechanic and the person who likes aquamarine##2
3. the mechanic is the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
5. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
6. the mechanic is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the dancer is the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the person who likes azure is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday      | september   | february          | november | april        |
| Job   | doctor     | paramedic | mechanic   | dancer     |
| Color           | aquamarine | ivory         | chestnut         | azure |

