.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, ice-hockey, rugby, golf
4 different pets are kept: snake, ferret, goldfish, fish
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, italian, chinese, spanish
1. the spanish is on the left or right of the chinese##3
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the owner of the fish is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the chinese##1
5. the italian is between the owner of the snake and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the spanish is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
7. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
8. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is rugby##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | soccer      | rugby       | golf    |
| Pet           | ferret  | goldfish  | fish | snake |
| Nationality   | spanish      | chinese | italian         | argentine    |

