.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, skydiving, card-games, writing
There 4 different types of food: tomato, kale, apricot, pomegranate
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, blood-red, aquamarine, yellow
1. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
6. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
7. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
8. the person eating kale is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
9. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving         | baking  | card-games     | writing         |
| Food        | pomegranate | kale | tomato | apricot         |
| Color      | blood-red         | aquamarine  | mauve   | yellow |

