.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, dancing, drawing, writing
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, aquamarine, emerald, purple
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, bus, ship, helicopter
 1. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
 2. the person who likes ivory is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is singing##2
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 6. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 7. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
10. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing  | drawing    | dancing | writing    |
| Color   | ivory | emerald | aquamarine  | purple |
| Transport           | ship   | helicopter    | van        | bus   |

