.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, zombie, drama, superhero
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, frog, cat
City: berlin, marseilles, new-york, boston
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
4. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
8. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
9. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre      | adventure                | superhero  | zombie | drama   |
| Pet           | cat | rat | goldfish   | frog |
| City   | marseilles         | berlin     | boston     | new-york |

