.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, project-manager, social-worker, entrepreneur
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, azalea, daisy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, golf, biathlon, skiing
1. the project-manager is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
2. the social-worker is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
4. the social-worker is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who's sport is skiing##2
6. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
7. the journalist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Job          | social-worker    | project-manager  | entrepreneur  | journalist |
| Flower   | daisy | iris | tulip | azalea |
| Sport   | biathlon    | cricket     | skiing    | golf |

