.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, ritmeester, dannemann, bongani
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, video-games, sudoku, dancing
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, nurse, fisherman, security-guard
1. the nurse is between the dannemann-smoker and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the security-guard is in an odd position##4
6. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the pall-mall-smoker##1
9. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the fisherman and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar      | pall-mall | dannemann      | ritmeester  | bongani    |
| Hobby   | sudoku   | video-games | dancing | traveling |
| Job           | security-guard      | fisherman       | nurse   | videographer      |

