.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bus, ship, van
City: new-york, hamburg, berlin, miami
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, classical, gospel, metal
1. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the van and the fan of rock##2
3. the fan of classical is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
6. the person traveling to miami is between the fan of rock and the person traveling to new-york##2
7. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
9. the fan of rock is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Transport         | train    | ship | bus  | van  |
| City   | berlin | hamburg       | miami | new-york |
| Music-Genre         | gospel   | rock      | metal | classical       |

