.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia, rose, iris
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, tram, van, quad-bike
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, domino, mah-jongg
1. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
2. the person playing billiard is the person who growszinnia##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person who growsrose is the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the car is the person playing billiard##1
7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
8. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Flower      | rose      | zinnia | balloon-flower     | iris    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | car      | tram | van |
| Game           | domino   | billiard  | scrabble     | mah-jongg |

