4. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the designer##3
5. the architect is between the owner of the cat and the person who likes purple##2
6. the owner of the lizard is the person who likes lilac##1
7. the architect is on the left of the journalist##1
8. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
