The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, photography, singing
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, trike, helicopter, van
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the trike and the havana-smoker##2
