4. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4
7. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
8. the havana-smoker is the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Cigar          | old-henry | havana  | baccarat   | pall-mall    |
| Hobby   | drawing  | photography     | singing | hiking |
| Transport   | helicopter   | van | subway | trike   |

