4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
5. the cain-smoker is the person playing billiard##1
6. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person playing poker##1
7. the person playing poker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
8. the person who likes purple is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Cigar   | dunhill | game | cain | montecristo   |
| Color   | purple    | ivory   | yellow     | emerald    |
| Game   | go  | poker | billiard  | canasta |

