.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, go, bridge
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, american, italian, indonesian
City: rome, edinburgh, hamburg, paris
1. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
2. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
4. the person playing go is on the far left##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is between the indonesian and the malaysian##2
6. the american is on the left of the malaysian##1
7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Game    | go    | mah-jongg    | scrabble  | bridge |
| Nationality   | indonesian | american | malaysian | italian      |
| City     | edinburgh   | rome        | paris   | hamburg       |

 